                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-06-19</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book provides an excellent model to evaluate the availability of your data network. The tools provided in this book are straight forward and easily understood. If your network is critical to business, and especially if your voice traffic is running over it, you need this book. This book was written as something to use, not just to read.</span>
                  
              
